    "Moreover, the best result was obtained for optimally configured DNN with five layers i.e.",
    "L = 5, and 20 and 30 neurons in each hidden layer.",
    "The same results are also obtained for L = 4 and N h = 30.",
    "That is, the proposed approach can classify subjects as PD and healthy with an accuracy of 100%.",
    "The results of the experiment are reported in Table 3."
